title: Trades We'd Like To See Happen
itunes:title: Trades We'd Like To See Happen
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Colleen Wolfe, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler- assemble for a Sans-Dan show. The heroes discuss the latest news from around the league, including the Jets' reported interest in free agent QB Kirk Cousins (4:00), Doug Martin being released by Tampa Bay (9:00), Marcus Peters on the trade block and Peyton Manning being pursued by ESPN and FOX (17:00); Colleen presents a combine version of Odds & Ends, along with a new spin on the Odds & Ends theme song (25:00); And the heroes each pitch one trade they'd like to see happen (33:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
